sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL / PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP SQL
    participant K8s as K8s API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows
    participant Driver as V2 Driver<br/>(sidecar step)
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-service<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as V2 Launcher<br/>(in user container)
    participant S3 as SeaweedFS / MinIO<br/>9000/TCP S3 API
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution (V2)

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run record<br/>Username/Password
    API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Schedule Workflow

    Argo->>Driver: Execute driver step<br/>(process exec)
    Driver->>MLMD: Create execution record<br/>gRPC (optional TLS)
    Driver->>API: Cache key lookup<br/>gRPC/8887 (optional TLS)
    alt Cache miss
        Argo->>Launcher: Execute user container<br/>(process exec)
        Launcher->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Access Key auth
        Note over Launcher: Execute pipeline component
        Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Access Key auth
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish results<br/>gRPC (optional TLS)
    else Cache hit
        Note over Driver: Skip execution,<br/>inject cached outputs
    end

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow status<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status update
    PA->>API: Report metrics & status<br/>gRPC/8887 ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 2: Recurring Run Scheduling

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringRuns<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store recurring run<br/>Username/Password
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    SWC->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over SWC: Cron/periodic trigger fires
    SWC->>API: CreateRun gRPC<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API->>K8s: Submit Argo Workflow<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 3: Cache Hit (V1 Pod Mutation)

    K8s->>API: Admission webhook call<br/>HTTPS/8443 mTLS
    Note over API: Cache Server (/mutate)
    API->>DB: Lookup cache key<br/>Username/Password
    alt Cache hit
        API-->>K8s: Patch pod spec<br/>inject cached outputs
    else Cache miss
        API-->>K8s: Allow pod creation<br/>no mutation
    end
